data.description: WOW! As one of the largest homes in this community, this home is perfect for entertaining or a big family. Beautiful double door entry where the foyer opens into a HUGE family rm w/cathedral ceilings. Split plan w/ HUGE master suite incl double entry, sitting area, jetted tub & bidet. Gourmet kitchen opens to living room w/ floor to ceiling fireplace. A wall of doors leads you to the oversized enclosed pool area looking out onto the 1-acre property w/lush landscaping. Community tennis and basketball courts. Lit streets. Don't miss out of this unique gem in a gated community. pool area has a spa, a gazebo, an outside kitchen and a bar for entertaining. one of the outbuildings is a workshop. the pool is sola heated..This is the one with everything you could need or want. A beautiful oasis in a desirable location in central Florida. As you approach the property you will find a very well-manicured property with a special driveway that does not need cleaning. As you enter your dream home through the 10-foot doors you will enter a large cathedral Family/dining room, this 4-bedroom 4 full bath home has a desirable split floor plan. The chef's Delite kitchen with its custom-made cabinets is the center of the living and dining room. The extra-large master bedroom w/ setting area, wall-in closet and bath w/jetted tub and walk in shower. As you enter the back patio you will walk into paradise with an outside kitchen, Bar, Gazebo, solar heated saltwater pool with specially designed spa. Outside the Lania covered patio you enter the one ac. Area with 6foot Vinyl fence surrounding a green house, a raised Garder with paved walkways totally fence in, and workshop. The property has 9 zones of irrigation with over 50 heads. It has a new well so there are no water bills. This paradise is a must see for the family looking for the perfect home in a gated community. There is a concrete pad for RV or boat. This home has so many upgrades we can’t list them all.
